## How to audit the code in 15 minutes

1. Unzip the bundle.
2. Open `setup_and_run.R` in any text editor. Read the labelled sections.
3. Open `analysis.R` (your project's R script).
4. Open `START_HERE.command` (or `.bat` / `.sh`) — each is ~110 lines, just invokes `Rscript`.
5. Grep for the usual red flags:
   ```
   grep -nE 'system|shell|exec|eval|curl|wget|chmod|sudo|rm |unlink' *.sh *.R
   ```

